name: Princess Delivery - Game Jam Version
description: We're an indie team working on a larger project, but we decided to take a weekend and make a fun, relaxing game in under 50 hours, game jam style! We will do our best to patch the bugs and add some additional planned content that did not make it in over the next few weeks. We may turn this into a small full release, so please let us know if you enjoyed it. Check out our main project here!
